snippet.title: Amber Heard--The Shortest Straw She Can Grasp At
snippet.description:
Continued commentary on the Johnny Depp/Amber Heard lawsuit; Amber's response to Johnny's detailed description of abuse he alleges she did to him.  I find it funny that all she could focus on were the 911 calls and who made them, rather than all the other overwhelming evidence Johnny Depp revealed.  Again, detailed research on this case is what drives me to keep speaking up for Johnny Depp as the victim and survivor of what was indeed a toxic and abusive marriage.
